videos.title: Crispy October mornin' on Dirty Sheets
videos.description:
Took a little bit more camera gear out on the trail this time to capture some of the beauty this chilly fall morning in Atlanta had to offer. 

The gravel bike gang is growing! It was Nick's first time out on proper gravel with the brand new Specialized Diverge 👌

videos.title: Cyclepaths Dirty Sheets Ride
videos.description:
The Cyclepaths Group Recovery ride 2-26-23
We had 20+ riders come out for this social no-drop ride and we had a blast! 

Dirty Sheets is located west of Atlanta in Chattahoochee Hills GA. 
Route https://ridewithgps.com/trips/114236840

Music by Tabletopaudio.com
